                  </tr><tr>
                          <th> </th><th>9</th><td class="r"><ins></ins> </td>
                  </tr><tr>
                          <th> </th><th>10</th><td class="r"><ins>To create a backup of a live TracEnvironment, simply run:</ins> </td>
                  </tr><tr>
                          <th> </th><th>11</th><td class="r"><ins>{{{</ins> </td>
                  </tr><tr>
